references.paper_title: HQG-Net: Unpaired medical image enhancement with high-quality guidance
references.reason: This paper is foundational to the current work, providing a method for high-quality image guidance which is adapted for the current dehazing task.

references.paper_title: Single image haze removal using dark channel prior
references.reason: This is a highly influential and foundational paper in the field of image dehazing, establishing a baseline technique which is improved upon in the current work.

references.paper_title: Proximal dehaze-net: A prior learning-based deep network for single image dehazing
references.reason: This paper introduced the concept of unfolding networks to image dehazing which is the basis of the current cooperative unfolding network.

references.paper_title: RIDCP: Revitalizing real image dehazing via high-quality codebook priors
references.reason: This paper is directly related to the current work, focusing on real image dehazing and achieving state-of-the-art results which are improved upon by the current work.

references.paper_title: Deep generalized unfolding networks for image restoration
references.reason: This paper provides a generalized framework for unfolding networks used for image restoration which is used to inform the current cooperative unfolding network.
